- 종료
docker-compose down

-----------------------

- Confluent JDBC 플러그인 다운로드
https://www.confluent.io/hub/confluentinc/kafka-connect-jdbc

- MySQL 커넥터 드라이버 다운로드
wget https://dev.mysql.com/get/Downloads/Connector-J/mysql-connector-java-8.0.22.tar.gz

-----------------------

